Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.74,0:01:30.14,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2\c&H9262F8&}请{\c&HDFC73A&}你{\c}不要撇开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:33.79,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1aFE\shad5}全部見てほしい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.14,0:01:33.79,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\c&H9262F8&}全{\c&HDFC73A&}部{\c}見てほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:33.79,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1aFE\shad5}认真看着我的一切
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.14,0:01:33.79,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\c&H9262F8&}认{\c&HDFC73A&}真{\c}看着我的一切
